趣<br />\n我就算話比人聽我識日文鍾意日本文化<br />\n都係比人話9我死毒撚<br />\n唔使理,我繼續開心睇日劇聽J-POP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e5980445f5f2fe9d22c56357387787c8ea541a","tid":118443,"uid":71819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"白淺上神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0606e8162ef4e0c9afdb72595478d11d99bcb310","tid":118443,"uid":59053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:35:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打機，睇動漫，但依D 唔計興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有女問你你都唔敢咁答啦<br />\nbtw我連打機睇動漫我都冇興趣"},{"pid":"252d774a290c9ab9cf71d8c2414b4f45f5d03fa9","tid":118443,"uid":59053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>定係你想問有冇人零正面興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你都可以咁講既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔使咁介懷呢D既<br />\n我都無咩特別比人聽落型既興趣<br />\n我就算話比人聽我識日文鍾意日本文化<br />\n都係比人話9我死毒撚<br />\n唔使理,我繼續開心睇日劇聽J-POP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果鍾意日本文化去到好深入，都唔差"},{"pid":"a18e44e322242dffffcce8a693a8ab6c16cf598f","tid":118443,"uid":59053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白淺上神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好努力睇到第十集only<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a329faf47cbbb74e7ced2d1786dd72da45f728","tid":118443,"uid":51512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T07:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以溝唔到女"},{"pid":"2e68dad36a950d2be9ca8dfcc78278628947f232","tid":118443,"uid":60635,